		<h2>Card Layout</h2>
		<p>A card should have the following structure to achieve the layout shown below.</p>

		<pre style="background-color: #eee;padding: 1em;">
&lt;div class="layout-card"&gt;
	&lt;button class="close"&gt;
		&lt;i class="fa fa-times" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;
		&lt;span class="aria-text"&gt;Close&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;/button&gt;
	&lt;div class="label-info"&gt;
		&lt;div class="row"&gt;
			&lt;div class="columns small-12"&gt;
				&lt;h2 class="label-heading"&gt;
					&lt;div class="label-title"&gt;
						&lt;span class="label-brandName"&gt;Aspirin Adult low strength&lt;/span&gt;
						&lt;span class="label-genericName"&gt;(ASPIRIN)&lt;/span&gt;
					&lt;/div&gt;
					&lt;div class="label-manufacturer"&gt;Valu Merchandisers Company (Best Choice)&lt;/div&gt;
				&lt;/h2&gt;
			&lt;/div&gt;
		&lt;/div&gt;
		&lt;div class="row label-recall"&gt;
			&lt;div class="columns small-12"&gt;
				&lt;i class="fa fa-exclamation-circle" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;
				&lt;span class="label-recall-text"&gt;
					This item is currently under a 
					&lt;span class="label-recall-badge"&gt;
						Class II &lt;i class="fa fa-info-circle" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;
					&lt;/span&gt; 
					recall.
				&lt;/span&gt;
				&lt;button class="label-openRecall"&gt;
					RECALL REPORT &lt;i class="fa fa-chevron-right" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;
				&lt;/button&gt;
			&lt;/div&gt;
		&lt;/div&gt;
		&lt;div class="row"&gt;
			&lt;div class="columns small-12"&gt;
				&lt;h3 class="label-warning"&gt;
					&lt;i class="fa fa-warning" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;/i&gt; Pregnant or Nursing Mothers
				&lt;/h3&gt;
				&lt;p&gt;
					If pregnant or breast- feeding, ask a health professional before use. 
					It is especially important not to use aspirin during the last 3 months 
					of pregnancy unless definitely directed to do so by a doctor because 
					it may cause problems in the unborn child or complications during delivery.
				&lt;/p&gt;

				&lt;p&gt;
					&lt;span class="label-badge"&gt;Dosage&lt;/span&gt;Directions do not exceed 
					recommended dosage drink a full glass of water with each dose adults and 
					children 12 years of age and over: take 4 to 8 tablets every 4 hours not 
					to exceed 48 tablets in 24 hours, unless directed by a doctor children under 
					12 years of age: consult a doctor
				&lt;/p&gt;
				&lt;button class="label-control"&gt;
					Full Details &lt;i class="fa fa-chevron-right" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;
				&lt;/button&gt;
			&lt;/div&gt;
		&lt;/div&gt;
	&lt;/div&gt;
